{"tid":547874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香 港 人 連 立 足 嘅 地 方 都 無","createTime":"2018-02-02T02:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T14:15:30.000Z","uid":10292,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"27a54a06cf4b8ba331424c808ff84e31dd0ce225","tid":547874,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T02:30:04.000Z","msg":"朝早搭狗鐵逼到仆街就眾所鳩知<br />\n由美孚逼到去太子，再由太子逼到九龍塘先叫可以鬆口氣<br />\n車廂終於走咁啲人，滿心歡喜咁挨住塊玻璃當自己有得坐嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n響樂富上左一對廢老，一黎就捉住玻璃隔離條扶手，背向我一直向我個方向逼逼逼，一開頭見都幾廿歲忍下啦，屌你老母變本加厲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 逼鳩到我無位企<br />\n<br />\n我講左句 : 咁撚鍾意逼你自己逼鳩爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講完之後佢若無其事咁企埋落我個位<br />\n<br />\n作為一個普通嘅香港人，我都只係想搭地鐵有位企下，平時出街唔洗寸步難行。但偏偏就俾蝗搞到家不成家，一車車嘅新移民，水貨客，破壞緊香港原有嘅生活。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好簡單一個例子，細細個同老母行街好開心，可以周圍跳周圍跑，唔驚撞到人。<br />\n依家出街呀，唔洗同人身貼身已經係皇恩浩蕩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港人係咪真係要俾人逼到無立足之地先會醒覺<br />\n如果你話唔想做前線<br />\n不如嘗試下做多啲，好似捐錢俾義士，實有樣野做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76ada8c0191325ff6895f0a03c0a7c8f86ac93c","tid":547874,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:09:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7478881e66739e5944f1a035b90436dc12fae4e4","tid":547874,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:37:57.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582823b05fcfe13aa88109c173466302ce984ef8","tid":547874,"uid":10292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7478881e66739e5944f1a035b90436dc12fae4e4","tid":547874,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:37:57.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:40:11.000Z","msg":"就係一開頭寬恕得太多，俾班仆街入侵<br />\n諗返起都想屌佢老味臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09095d832e3aaaf88f892e05cd0e5a5c8b65e931","tid":547874,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:40:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6ccfecdc5aa440c354b442e79abaac85f31523","tid":547874,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:40:29.000Z","msg":"有後路走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e687f727e1b428ee59ba297462f8ba691f477b6","tid":547874,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:57:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8629afb7188f3c2542d34fd1f02cb8fcf5d9373","tid":547874,"uid":81256,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:58:19.000Z","msg":"咁又點<br />\n樓主有咩良策？"},{"pid":"db14e03f4c21ab7342137869980a723485f9882c","tid":547874,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a8629afb7188f3c2542d34fd1f02cb8fcf5d9373","tid":547874,"uid":81256,"